A man has been given the disgrace of a lifetime after he was publicly flogged for trying to sleep with his brother’s wife. It was gathered that the man came all the way from Imo state to Abia state just to sleep with his brother’s wife. The people who caught him asked him why he wanted to sleep with the brother’s wife, but he told them that his intention was just to talk with her. They kept flogging him asking him to say the truth and threatening to kill him. They revealed that the name of the brother is Izuchukwu. The man later confessed that he traveled all the way from Imo to Abia state in order to sleep with the brother’s wife. See video below: Source